title: Ep. 46 :: It's A Girl!
itunes:title: It's A Girl!
description: Frank talks about being a dad again. Also, he tells you to ignore the talking heads on CNBC. Buying stocks at these levels - ahead of earnings season is a death wish. Finally - Frank provides pictures and videos from his business trip to China.
